on a chain gang."

23:01.848 --> 23:03.884
You hear music?

23:03.917 --> 23:05.151
Ask the boy.

23:05.185 --> 23:06.753
Ask him.

23:06.787 --> 23:08.789
Leon fought‐‐ he fought hard.

23:08.822 --> 23:10.991
OPAL:
He shouldn't have
been out there at all.

23:12.693 --> 23:15.161
Boss's son.

23:15.195 --> 23:16.963
Underage.

23:16.997 --> 23:20.734
Neck deep in liquor
and syphilis.

23:22.603 --> 23:24.771
I'm fucked.

23:26.072 --> 23:28.408
