is a crime story.

25:00.901 --> 25:03.003
But here's the rub.

25:03.036 --> 25:06.607
When we hear a crime story,
who do we root for?

25:06.640 --> 25:10.076
Not the poor sap that got taken.

25:10.110 --> 25:11.878
The victim, no.

25:11.912 --> 25:14.615
We root for the taker.

25:14.648 --> 25:17.283
The guy with the gat.

25:17.317 --> 25:19.185
(imitating machine gun)

25:25.726 --> 25:28.228
See, this country loves a man

25:28.261 --> 25:31.297
who takes what he wants.

25:31.331 --> 25:33.867
Unless...

25:35.802 --> 25:38.038
(whispers):
Unless that man looks like you.

25:43.109 --> 25:45.846
Capisce?

25:45.879 --> 25:48.314
See, Johnny Society looks at me,

25:48.348 --> 25:51.952
they see a fella
that's using crime to get ahead.

25:51.985 --> 25:54.354
But you?

25:54.387 --> 25:57.323
All they see is crime.

25:57.357 --> 26:00.961
And that's why
you're gonna lose.

26:00.994 --> 26:03.797
'Cause I can take all the money

26:03.830 --> 26:06.199
and pussy I want

26:06.232 --> 26:09.670
and still run for president.

26:09.703 --> 26:11.304
But you?

26:12.973 --> 26:15.676
It's always gonna be the rope.

26:17.644 --> 26:20.213
Tell him it's time to surrender.

26:34.260 --> 26:36.396
What's he gonna do?

26:36.429 --> 26:38.865
Loy.

26:38.899 --> 26:41.835
Man, go fuck yourself.

26:41.868 --> 26:43.403
MILLIGAN:
We don't have time for that.

26:43.436 --> 26:45.138
This is about his boy.

26:45.171 --> 26:47.240
What's the man gonna do?

26:47.273 --> 26:49.142
Settle or war?

26:49.175 --> 26:50.611
The devil lives in the past.

26:52.445 --> 26:54.881
Ain't no going back
to the way it was.

26:58.151 --> 27:00.887
Tell him I'll keep the boy safe.

27:00.921 --> 27:02.989
No matter what.

27:03.023 --> 27:05.158
OPAL:
You just bring him back home.

27:05.191 --> 27:08.128
‐We'll watch him.
‐No.

27:08.161 --> 27:10.631
You're all gonna die.

27:34.888 --> 27:36.422
(knocking)

27:36.456 --> 27:38.124
Buzz off.

27:38.158 --> 27:41.394
DEAFY:
It's me, Palomino. Open up.

27:41.427 --> 27:42.963
(exhales)

27:49.803 --> 27:52.138
(knocking and grunting
rhythmically)

27:56.977 --> 27:58.178
Rough night?

27:58.211 --> 28:01.181
(exhales)
