we're partners.

28:11.091 --> 28:14.427
So, anything you need.
¿Comprendo?

28:14.460 --> 28:16.362
We're not partners.

28:16.396 --> 28:17.964
Hey.

28:17.998 --> 28:20.000
Hey, that's private.

28:23.103 --> 28:24.304
Guessing the story
didn't end well

28:24.337 --> 28:26.439
for the girl in the picture.

28:26.472 --> 28:28.441
No, she died.

28:28.474 --> 28:29.943
Wife?

28:30.977 --> 28:32.312
Intended.

28:32.345 --> 28:34.247
While I was overseas.

28:34.280 --> 28:36.082
Criminy.

28:36.116 --> 28:37.483
How'd she go?

28:37.518 --> 28:39.052
What?

28:39.085 --> 28:41.454
I said "How did she go?"

28:41.487 --> 28:44.024
If you don't mind me asking.
(sniffles)

28:46.159 --> 28:48.995
Nelson Beets.

28:49.029 --> 28:50.864
Broke in while she was sleeping.

28:50.897 --> 28:53.066
Raped her, strangled her
with her own panties.

28:54.267 --> 28:55.836
(Odis sighs)

29:01.908 --> 29:03.409
I got the letter
while I was in France.

29:03.443 --> 29:04.845
(liquid pouring)

29:04.878 --> 29:06.112
(sets bottle down)

29:06.146 --> 29:08.114
Well, they had me clearing
land mines...

29:08.148 --> 29:10.884
on account I'm real precise.

29:10.917 --> 29:14.087
Get a system, never vary.

29:14.120 --> 29:16.890
Meanwhile, other guys
are getting distracted,

29:16.923 --> 29:19.425
blowing themselves
to smithereens.

29:19.459 --> 29:21.261
(exhales)

29:21.294 --> 29:23.530
Anyway, got the letter
one morning.

29:23.564 --> 29:27.033
Went out to clear a field.

29:27.067 --> 29:29.402
Just laid down
right there in the grass.

29:32.205 --> 29:34.808
Must've been there
three, four hours.

29:40.914 --> 29:42.883
You know, I swear...

29:42.916 --> 29:45.151
the clouds look different
over there.

29:45.185 --> 29:47.521
Different how?

29:50.190 --> 29:52.158
I don't know. French, I guess.

29:57.598 --> 30:00.133
What was her name?

30:01.334 --> 30:03.303
Was there something you needed?

30:03.336 --> 30:06.172
No. Just, uh...

30:06.206 --> 30:09.042
I had a vision
last night is all,

30:09.075 --> 30:11.144
while I was saying my prayers.

30:12.345 --> 30:14.280
"Shake the tree," said the Lord.

30:14.314 --> 30:17.050
"And your suspects shall fall
like sweet, ripe fruit."

30:17.083 --> 30:18.585
So that's what I'm gonna do.

30:18.619 --> 30:20.887
Thought you might want
to shake it with me.

30:20.921 --> 30:22.322
I got to...

30:22.355 --> 30:25.191
There's a lot of paperwork.
Big raid, you know?

30:25.225 --> 30:27.027
Captain said, "Stick with Odis.
He'll be your guide."

30:27.060 --> 30:29.563
Yeah, but you been here,
what, 25 years now?

30:29.596 --> 30:32.232
I'm surprised they ain't
named a street after you.

30:32.265 --> 30:34.300
You'll be fine.

30:37.270 --> 30:39.305
Okeydokey.

30:41.007 --> 30:44.177
Well, I'll let you know
if anything comes out of my day.

30:46.112 --> 30:48.214
Yeah. You do that.

30:50.483 --> 30:52.452
(woman singing opera)

31:01.361 --> 31:03.429
