32:20.206 --> 32:22.242
(Gaetano sighs)

32:25.579 --> 32:27.047
(man sighs)

32:27.080 --> 32:28.481
CALAMITA:
He thinks he can

32:28.515 --> 32:32.452
scare them, your brother,
like it's Halloween

32:32.485 --> 32:35.522
and we're kids
with our trick or treat.

32:44.631 --> 32:46.600
How Josto scare them?

32:50.737 --> 32:53.039
The more important is,

32:53.073 --> 32:55.108
you scare an animal,
you don't know.

32:55.141 --> 32:56.743
Sometimes it fights.

32:56.777 --> 32:58.745
You have to kill it.

33:05.218 --> 33:07.487
Boss, I'm trying to...

33:07.521 --> 33:09.389
We got to make a move.

33:09.422 --> 33:11.091
A real move.

33:11.124 --> 33:13.459
Hey.

33:13.494 --> 33:15.729
Chaplin, come...

33:18.665 --> 33:20.133
What is this?

33:20.166 --> 33:23.670
It's‐‐ what you‐‐ c‐coffee.

33:23.704 --> 33:25.338
That's what you call this?

33:25.371 --> 33:29.743
Yeah, with, uh,
it looks like milk and sugar.

33:31.778 --> 33:33.714
Milk and sugar?

33:36.783 --> 33:38.484
(Gaetano sighs)

33:38.519 --> 33:42.122
You know what's wrong
with this country, hmm?

33:42.155 --> 33:45.759
Your Jesus...
looks like a lady, hmm?

33:45.792 --> 33:47.494
And everybody thinks

33:47.528 --> 33:49.295
