34:36.877 --> 34:39.713
because your lady Jesus tell you

34:39.746 --> 34:41.848
that I'm gonna turn
the other cheek.

34:44.751 --> 34:47.721
Well...
(exhales)

34:49.389 --> 34:51.424
I'm Italian.

34:52.391 --> 34:54.360
And in Italy,

34:54.393 --> 34:57.430
they had to nail our Jesus
to the cross.

34:58.398 --> 35:00.734
Otherwise, he comes down

35:00.767 --> 35:04.605
and kill every last motherfucker
in Jerusalem.

