37:19.472 --> 37:21.742
She turns 17 today.

37:21.775 --> 37:24.745
So, that's, um...

37:24.778 --> 37:27.447
So, how you been?

37:27.480 --> 37:29.750
It's been a long night, Thurman.

37:29.783 --> 37:31.585
Don't try my patience.

37:31.618 --> 37:35.021
DIBRELL:
Mr. Cannon, I swear,
whatever it is,

37:35.055 --> 37:37.357
we can fix it.

37:37.390 --> 37:39.626
LOY:
You paid me back

37:39.660 --> 37:41.327
with my own money.

37:42.663 --> 37:43.897
We...

37:43.930 --> 37:45.566
You robbed my place,

37:45.599 --> 37:47.968
your proxy shot
a couple of my guys,

37:48.001 --> 37:49.503
and then you turn around

37:49.536 --> 37:51.638
