38:19.065 --> 38:20.901
Well...

38:24.070 --> 38:25.772
Tell them your name.

38:25.806 --> 38:29.009
Zirominu Guglielmo Fadda.

38:29.042 --> 38:32.378
I traded for him.

38:32.412 --> 38:33.680
You...

38:33.714 --> 38:37.684
I traded my own son to my enemy
for power.

38:37.718 --> 38:41.387
