at night, but me?

38:41.421 --> 38:42.689
I sleep like a baby.

38:42.723 --> 38:45.025
You understand?

38:45.058 --> 38:49.395
I will do
whatever it takes to win.

38:51.431 --> 38:53.066
Yes, sir.

39:00.741 --> 39:02.809
Get the boy a piece of cake.

