"Whatever you want, boss.

39:59.866 --> 40:01.467
Just don't kill me."

40:01.502 --> 40:03.870
Also, you're gonna tell me
where your sister's at.

40:05.205 --> 40:07.173
Oh, yeah,
I've been doing some asking.

40:07.207 --> 40:10.043
Zelmare Roulette.

40:10.076 --> 40:12.579
(chuckles softly)
Some name.

40:12.613 --> 40:14.781
Her and her butch Indian.

40:14.815 --> 40:18.051
They broke out of prison
and now they're here.

40:18.084 --> 40:19.720
Well, I want 'em.

40:20.754 --> 40:22.723
What are you gonna do?

40:23.757 --> 40:26.026
Whatever the fuck I want.

40:26.059 --> 40:28.028
‐It's my fault.
‐Thurman.

40:28.061 --> 40:30.664
No.

40:30.697 --> 40:33.166
I should've asked her
where she got the...

40:33.199 --> 40:37.037
But... it's my first time, see?

40:37.070 --> 40:39.039
Owing money to a...

40:40.073 --> 40:42.676
And I didn't...

40:42.709 --> 40:45.178
